title: RHONJ: Dog & Ponytail Show
description:
It's the fight that everyone's been talking about on Real Housewives of New Jersey: Marge pours water on Danielle's head, Danielle yanks Marge's ponytail. Old school stripper fighting. Plus, Frankie Jr. walks in Melissa's Envy fashion show, and Jackie teaches us about yogurt.
Get tix to our live shows: http://watchwhatcrappens.com

See acast.com/privacy for privacy and opt-out information.
